  "unresolvedTextByHash": {
    "8a410ca03797e9bfb0bc669081bef916a569b0c8c07a26620622f507c0f238df": "I'll meet you back at the Jolly Boar Inn, [?].",
    "105f75ca32523ce584ad9b5f68b4257e5509de36b380eec277e51f99ecc0fa9a": "I'm afraid that's not all, Captain. [?] has made some further discoveries.",
    "7bee6c411ad5940c53afde74d2079cdd09dbbecab3d3eac972b568311fad3150": "You'd better head over to Camdozaal, [?]. Time is not on our side.",
    "f07ec1536a1168f1ae785b05d653954a16fc57cd2ffb2df748e17145a5bee3b1": "Have you managed to make any progress, [?]?",
    "243f44aeb5f58774a0ba4a8d182a225be0fe84bc5d419c49b4ab6a6648665de9": "Ah, hello there, [?]. Good to see you.",
    "7a3881c9c65600fc6e070dc1c14633fdc1a9ee1d20141ce1e94b585be6e996e8": "Ah, hello there, [?]. Good to see you. I take it you recived my message?",
    "d3b1cd0b2087f7ba6735900df3c972fbb8c858ea5e4b920d8de93aec19543988": "Ah, hello again, [?]. How goes the tomb raiding?",
    "a01e3fe62a6208ca2aa1a0d5fbd36f7f906da5d4ab1cca60597be6972ec8c521": "Hello again, [?]. Have you managed to explore those tunnels yet?",
    "a6267ee2eb1bb6a63356343a456b2d7cc2b32c341a35e01ee39e11ef8913875e": "Hello again, [?]. Did you manage to find a way into that fort?",
    "aaa54b21fff6ea1614af187113420e84fff15f69307b7b3b90669f8c881ab7cc": "Hello again, [?]. I found this earlier. I imagine you'll be needing it.",
    "3a27d2b18b7e09f6d0aa145d786e302546ce9f2b9c8d006961085708132c375c": "Ah, there you are, [?]. Ready to perform a heist? Remember, you'll need some sort of insulated protection along with a crossbow and grappling hook.",
    "1a2222b690f6de357c00871f048a896d2f0c7469fee4795261aecebbb9cec8de": "I'm ready when you are, [?]. Once you head in, I'll arrange a distraction to lure some of those zombies away. I'll meet you back here once you've recovered the heart. Good luck.",
